data.description: Checkout this one of a kind home, beautifully updated while still offering a historic feel. Can be used as a Duplex with it having 2 separate levels & private entrances. Beautifully updated kitchen with granite countertops, quality cabinets, crown molding, beautiful wainscoting throughout formal dining room. Property has A LOT to offer whether for investment purposes or a large family. Furnace heat on 1st floor, and radiator works for 2nd floor.  All appliances are included. Book your showings while it's available!!
